data.message: working on a really cool music based project, which is totally out of my comfort zone.   the whole research exercise is provoking seemingly random observations like all natural drinks from beer to milk have colors that are either white or in the yellow to red range, none that are naturally blue.   another observation is that if i pick an odd number of q-tips i still have an even number of tips to clean each ear with.   same with an even number of picks. ...
